      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MALICIOUS (6) is a handy dog who jumped from box 1 last time out and scored by 1.5 lengths at The Gardens (29.77). Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Hard to fault his form and makes plenty of appeal again. PRINCE OF PERSIA (4) is having his first look at this course. Comes here after a last start 4th and beaten 8 lengths (35.15) at Gosford. Expected to run well. OLIVER GO (7) is a promising type who notched his 7th career success when too good (29.79) at this track last time. Has a good record here including six wins. Has won two of three starts from this draw. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. MALAWI REBEL (2) found the frame here last start and looks a top-three hope again.",
